      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single representative pump specimen used for bench validation.",
      "rationale": "A single pump specimen manufactured to nominal dimensions was used for bench validation. Sample-to-sample variability is not characterized at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
