      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD boundary conditions are shown to match experimental inlet/outlet conditions within documented measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles derived from ultrasonic flowmeter measurements were applied as CFD inlet boundary conditions. Outlet pressure was set to match measured back-pressure within 2 mmHg. Equivalency of all five operating-point input parameters is documented in TR-CPB-2024-001 Table 3."
    }
